== Events ==
[[File:Kameyama hachimangu shrine Summer festival.JPG|thumbnail|right|Kameyama Hachimangu Summer festival]]
*Hatsumode, Coming-of-Age ceremony, Omiyamairi, {{ill|Shichi-Go-San|ja|七五三参り|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Sasebo Kunchi|ja|佐世保くんち|12=draft|12=draft}}
*Summer festival - Held from August 1 to 3. Stalls and vendors are set up along the approach, and dances are performed on the stage within the shrine grounds. Until around 2010, fireworks were launched from the grounds of the adjacent {{ill|Sasebo Kita Junior High and High School|ja|長崎県立佐世保北中学校・高等学校|12=draft|12=draft}} at 9 PM on the first and last days, and Niagara fireworks were lit within the shrine grounds.

